If you mess around again,

00:37:04.952 --> 00:37:06.370
then I'll reveal this.

00:37:07.747 --> 00:37:08.831
Sis.

00:37:08.914 --> 00:37:10.207
Come on, don't do this.

00:37:10.916 --> 00:37:13.252
If that gets out,
you won't be safe either.

00:37:13.336 --> 00:37:15.379
You just need to keep your mouth shut.

00:37:15.963 --> 00:37:19.050
Just like what you've done until now.
Nothing else.

