00:40:17.645 --> 00:40:19.063
Nudge her in the right place,

00:40:19.146 --> 00:40:21.565
and she could overshadow
President-elect and Ms. Cha.

00:40:21.649 --> 00:40:22.816
Cheon U-hyeok!

