What? What?!

00:40:26.862 --> 00:40:28.656
You're trying to change the flow

00:40:28.739 --> 00:40:31.283
of the news that's moved on
to the special act

00:40:31.367 --> 00:40:32.535
back to Hwa-jin. Why?

00:40:32.618 --> 00:40:34.161
Check the viewers' comments.

00:40:34.245 --> 00:40:36.455
They're all about Lee Hwa-jin.

