and said you'd step down if you were found

00:42:47.503 --> 00:42:48.962
to be involved in the fire.

00:42:49.046 --> 00:42:51.674
I'll use every power I have

00:42:53.926 --> 00:42:55.552
to uncover the truth.

00:43:03.644 --> 00:43:04.978
