But sometimes, people with no common sense
can cause trouble.

00:44:20.929 --> 00:44:23.557
And when that happens,
things get out of control.

00:44:24.141 --> 00:44:25.350
Don't worry.

00:44:26.351 --> 00:44:30.022
The prosecutor in charge is Noh Cheol-jae,
and he's easily persuaded.

00:44:30.105 --> 00:44:32.232
I told him that he could join our party

00:44:32.316 --> 00:44:35.402
in the next general election
if he helped us with this.

00:44:35.486 --> 00:44:36.653
What about the evidence?

00:44:37.488 --> 00:44:40.157
It's still an investigation,
so it should look like one.

00:44:41.325 --> 00:44:42.701
We can just

00:44:42.785 --> 00:44:44.369
make evidence.

00:44:46.163 --> 00:44:47.831
H Chemical

